<DATELINE>PRAGUE, Czechoslovakia (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Twenty thousand fans lit candles
in a soccer stadium as Stevie Wonder brought pop rock to Prague in
a three-hour recital during his ``Peace Conversations'' tour.
   The blind American singer sang old hits such as ``Jammin,''
